2.5.0:
- Unify error messages, in that they now appear on STDERR.
- Increase maximum allowed password length to 1024
- Implement OpenSSH agent support to acquire a database password from a
  signature based on the chosen SSH private key. 'export'/'import' commands
  also support this.
- kc won't strip the last new-line character when reading the password from a
  file.
